data.description: NEW PRICE on this almost brand new home in The Preserve at Kitchin Farms!  5 minutes to I-540, and 5 min to charming shopping centers in Rolesville and Heritage! 15 minutes to Downtown Raleigh.  This almost new Mungo home is a perfect starter home or downsize option. It's absolutely gorgeous thanks to all of the seller's custom additions like shiplap, navy and white accents, crown molding, floating wood shelves, & LVP flooring! The upstairs Owner's Suite exudes R & R while one side of the Custom Walk-in Closet is set up for a great home office area. 3 bedrooms, 2.5 baths, a loft (that could be turned into 4th bedroom) + sunroom. This home feels "just right" and  offers extra space to gather and play in. The kitchen is a farmhouse dream with it's navy blue island, 5 burner gas range, pot filler, stainless farmhouse sink, pantry, and gorgeous island. The two secondary bedrooms are spacious & each have walk in closets. And for that all important outdoor space, look no further than your large fenced in backyard & garden box. Community Pool & Clubhouse! Wegmans, Target just 5 miles away too!
